74, \"to\": 1803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The smirk of a male who's knows he's protected by a misogynist sporting establishment enjoying the distress of a woman he's just punched in the head, and whose life's ambition he's just shattered.'\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 2011, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The smirk\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1823}, {\"ngram\": \"a male\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1833}, {\"ngram\": \"a misogynist sporting establishment\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1899}, {\"ngram\": \"the distress\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1921}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 1932}, {\"ngram\": \"the head\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1962}, {\"ngram\": \"whose life's ambition\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Musk, meanwhile, shared a post from American swimmer Riley Gaines which read: 'Men do not belong in women's sports'.\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2049, \"end\": 2057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999985621899545, \"rank\": 1.433204856840376e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2066, \"end\": 2071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Finn\", \"score\": 0.9999999165006591, \"rank\": 7.426860608158231e-08, \"text\": \"Riley\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Finn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Finn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Musk\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2017}, {\"ngram\": \"a post\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2043}, {\"ngram\": \"Men\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2095}, {\"ngram\": \"women's sports\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Musk added to the message by writing: 'Absolutely.'\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2181, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Musk\", \"from\": 2130